{"tid":2093913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約時報 : 川普長子女友確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-07-04T07:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T07:53:00.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e10b45ee1ac7de8106f12e5195c2d05564bb25b","tid":2093913,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普身邊又傳出有人確診感染武漢肺炎（COVID-19）病毒！《紐約時報》報導，川普長子、小唐納川普（Donald Trump Jr.）的女友吉佛耶（Kimberly Guilfoyle），其病毒檢測呈現陽性，而她也是川普身邊出現的第3個確診案例。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，就在川普預定於周五（7/3）晚間於拉什莫爾山（Mount Rushmore，又稱總統山）的國慶活動發表演說前，準備一起參加活動的小唐納和吉佛耶按照規定接受病毒檢測，沒想到吉佛耶的檢測結果呈現陽性，其他同行人員則都呈現陰性。<br />\n <br />\n據悉，吉佛耶並未出現任何病徵，也沒有接觸川普的隨行人員。為了確保第一家庭的安全，吉佛耶不得參加國慶活動，而小唐納也選擇和她一起搭車離開。<br />\n<br />\n..................<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200704/HJU4BLHECEIQZYO577R337KRMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200704%2FHJU4BLHECEIQZYO577R337KRMY%2F&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=55b77d48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200704%2FHJU4BLHECEIQZYO577R337KRMY%2F&h=89089a6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200704/HJU4BLHECEIQZYO577R337KRMY/</a>"},{"pid":"e1618055b176b99c9920662cadb41b44ebfdc138","tid":2093913,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"侵侵食的預防藥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvmrHFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvmrHFw.jpg&h=9baa5558&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}